Examples

days.found(string = "Lunch on Monday, tuesday, Wed, or Tursday?")
[1] "Monday"  "Tuesday"
days.found(string = "Appointment on thursdays")
[1] "Thursday"
days.found(string = "saturday, Saturdays, Friday, thursday, Wednesday, TueSday, Monday, SundaY")
[1] "Sunday"    "Monday"    "Tuesday"   "Wednesday" "Thursday"  "Friday"   
[7] "Saturday" 
days.found()
character(0)
days.found("When should we meet?")
character(0)
days.found("SaturdaySunday")
[1] "Sunday"   "Saturday"

p3 <- rank.plot(name = "Madison")

p4 <- rank.plot(name = "abcd")
